        "TileImage": "$($repository cafb2bda-485c-4c11-9df0-c1e6971dbbbb).Image",
        "Description": "Hello Agent 47, today your targets are located in Another Life. You are to eliminate three targets. Your first target is a spy disguised as jogger who is surveying the area to relay information. Your second target is Charles Blake III who has a political campaign. He cannot win and make the changes he plans to make. Your third target is Ms. Wilson whose insistent parties put Janus in jeopardy. Good luck, Agent 47.",
